CRTL-Z\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nObserve that the second part has become a seperate assembly\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003EVideo Evidence:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2024_06/KerbalSpaceProgram22024-06-1302-38-49.mp4.9a227a74b80eb70d766f255f65bd4f40.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221544\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1544\u0026amp;key=7485ded08e2a6e406d5353743a297060\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbal Space Program 2 2024-06-13 02-38-49.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-06-13T05:50:11Z\u0022 title=\u002206/13/2024 05:50  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jun 13\u0022\u003EJune 13\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}